	<section id="video-promo" class="help-people">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-8">
					<h2>Changing families <span>one man at a time&#153;</span></h2>
					<p class="message">When a teenager is the first to connect to a church, 3.5% of the time family follows. When a wife/mom is the first to connect to a church, 22% of the time the family follows. But when a man (husband/father) is the first to connect to a church, 93% of the time the family follows. Christian marriages end in divorce approximately 45% of the time. But when a man prays with his wife daily only 1 out of 1,152 marriages end in divorce; that's less than 0.1%! The Church needs to strategically focus its energy and resources on men to turn the tide of divorce, fatherlessness, and faithlessness.</p>

					<div class="video-section">
						<%= image_tag("graphics/wandering_in_desert.jpg", :data => {:video => 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/167131139'}) %> 
