					<h2>How you can help ? <span>See Below </span></h2>
					<div class="help-block">
						<h3><a href="/my_story"><%= image_tag("graphics/share_story.jpg") %>Share Your Story</a></h3>
						<p>Tell us about what Jesus Christ is doing in your life and how MDN has helped you grow closer to Him.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="help-block">
						<h3><a href="/jobslisting"><%= image_tag("graphics/muscle.jpg") %>Become Volunteer </a></h3>
						<p>Be part of something bigger than yourself. Join forces with a team committed to bringing God's Kingdom to men and their families. </p>
					</div>
					<div class="help-block">
						<h3><a href="/donate" data-toggle="modal">
							<%= image_tag("graphics/donation.jpg") %>Donate to MDN</a></h3>
						<p>Please support the work of God through MDN. We have much work to do, and need your financial support. Your donation is tax deductible. </p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
